<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Our Journey | Anniversary</title>
    <style>
        /* Base Styles ala Apple */
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body { 
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; 
            background-color: #fbfbfd; 
            color: #1d1d1f;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        /* Hero Section */
        .hero {
            height: 80vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            background: linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.3), rgba(255,255,255,0.3)), 
                        url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1518199266791-5375a83190b7?q=80&w=2070&auto=format&fit=crop'); /* Ganti dengan foto cover kalian */
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 56px;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: -0.015em;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .hero p {
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #515154;
            max-width: 600px;
        }

        /* Gallery Grid ala Apple Cards */
        .container {
            max-width: 1100px;
            margin: -100px auto 50px;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        .gallery-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 25px;
        }

        .card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 20px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .card:hover {
            transform: scale(1.02);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }

        .card img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 350px;
            object-fit: cover;
        }

        .card-content {
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .card-content h3 {
            font-size: 21px;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .card-content p {
            color: #86868b;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        /* Footer */
        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 100px 20px;
            background: #f5f5f7;
        }

        .heart-icon {
            color: #ff3b30;
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <section class="hero">
        <h1>WANDERLUST OF US.</h1>
        <p>Celebrating every chapter of our story.</p>
    </section>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="gallery-grid">
            <div class="card">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1516589174184-c68526674fd6?q=80&w=1974&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="Foto 1">
                <div class="card-content">
                    <h3>The Beginning</h3>
                    <p>Tempat pertama kita bertemu dan memulai segalanya.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1494774157365-9e04c6720e47?q=80&w=2070&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="Foto 2">
                <div class="card-content">
                    <h3>LDR Journey</h3>
                    <p>Jakarta - Bali bukan halangan buat kita.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1529634806980-85c3dd6d34ac?q=80&w=2070&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="Foto 3">
                <div class="card-content">
                    <h3>Future Dreams</h3>
                    <p>Membangun masa depan bersama, selangkah demi selangkah.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer>
        <div class="heart-icon">❤️</div>
        <p>Happy Anniversary, Nikia.</p>
        <p style="color: #86868b; font-size: 12px; margin-top: 10px;">Created with love using GitHub Pages</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
